Analysis on India Census Data 2011

Where is Indias population located?

  • Indias population is still in villages. All the next gen application and policies that we hear are available, visible and utilized by only 30%.

  • With constant droughts and floods impacting India especially the villages its about time for policy makers to review and heed the needs of Rural.

Religion wise population.

Now lets see the age percentages with their respective religion population.

Within males, Sikhs have the most senior citizens as they live for 80+ years. From 40+ , Jains are also seen consistently having high trends within their population.

Within females, Sikhs and Jains have the 80+ senior citizens. We also see Buddhist & Christians also showing high trends from 40+ years.
